1
00:00:06,570 --> 00:00:13,150
♪The neon lights before the French windows
shining at 3 AM♪

2
00:00:13,360 --> 00:00:18,650
♪The pile of old photos is getting dusty♪

3
00:00:19,290 --> 00:00:21,550
♪It's the season of reunion♪

4
00:00:21,550 --> 00:00:25,400
♪The gentle breeze is brushing my cheek♪

5
00:00:25,670 --> 00:00:31,870
♪You failed to see me in the crowd♪

6
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:38,500
♪The neon lights are bright,
but I can't find you in the crowd♪

7
00:00:38,660 --> 00:00:42,970
♪I can sense that you're avoiding me♪

8
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:46,500
♪On the empty street♪

9
00:00:46,820 --> 00:00:49,950
♪Where the neon lights are shining alone♪

10
00:00:50,370 --> 00:00:57,150
♪Just like our reunion♪

11
00:00:57,720 --> 00:01:03,400
♪The neon lights are blinking,
and I failed to get closer to you♪

12
00:01:03,710 --> 00:01:08,320
♪Some have already forgotten♪

13
00:01:08,370 --> 00:01:11,500
♪The fragments of memories♪

14
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:15,800
♪Will fade one day like neon lights♪

15
00:01:15,900 --> 00:01:21,220
♪By then, can we get the spark back?♪

16
00:01:25,720 --> 00:01:29,970
[To Be A Brave One]

17
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,950
[Episode 5]

18
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,440
Mr. Shao Moli.

19
00:01:54,510 --> 00:01:55,830
You made a name for yourself overseas,

20
00:01:55,830 --> 00:01:58,190
but this time, you returned to take up
a project from Wei'er Hotel.

21
00:01:58,190 --> 00:01:59,310
It is a resounding success so far.

22
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,080
What is your next plan?

23
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:03,040
Will you continue to stay here?

24
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:07,230
Even though I grew up overseas,

25
00:02:07,310 --> 00:02:09,830
I consider myself from Yuqing.

26
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,720
This city

27
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:13,630
contains many precious memories
from my childhood.

28
00:02:13,630 --> 00:02:14,670
And when I came back,

29
00:02:14,670 --> 00:02:16,670
I realized Yuqing had undergone major changes.

30
00:02:16,670 --> 00:02:19,960
It's now cozier, more mesmerizing.

31
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:22,320
It makes me fall in love further with the city

32
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,240
and the people who live there.

33
00:02:24,750 --> 00:02:27,270
I plan to stay,

34
00:02:28,190 --> 00:02:32,190
but there's one challenge in front of me.

35
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:36,360
I still can't handle chilies very well.

36
00:02:38,390 --> 00:02:39,720
How humorous of you.

37
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,110
The acquisition of Wei'er Hotel

38
00:02:41,190 --> 00:02:42,470
was flawlessly executed.

39
00:02:42,550 --> 00:02:44,630
I heard this project was an urgent one,

40
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:47,190
and you even encountered some difficulties.

41
00:02:47,190 --> 00:02:48,470
Can you tell us more?

42
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,520
When I took over this project,

43
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:51,110
it was,

44
00:02:51,110 --> 00:02:53,390
like you said, very tough.

45
00:02:53,390 --> 00:02:55,960
And we only had two months

46
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:57,830
to complete everything.

47
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:58,880
Fortunately,

48
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,470
I have a very talented team

49
00:03:00,550 --> 00:03:02,160
with good teamwork.

50
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,550
We had several emergencies,

51
00:03:04,550 --> 00:03:06,720
but we powered through them.

52
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:08,390
In this joint effort,

53
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:11,000
An Yu was the team leader.

54
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:14,830
She is competent, gifted,

55
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:17,240
and steadfast.

56
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:19,880
She was the key player

57
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:20,960
who turned the tide

58
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:22,960
when we were stuck in a pinch.

59
00:03:23,030 --> 00:03:23,720
Miss An.

60
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:25,880
Can you tell us the role you played

61
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,670
in this acquisition, as well as your feelings?

62
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:31,190
To good business.

63
00:03:32,110 --> 00:03:34,240
Mr. Shao here exaggerated my performance.

64
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:36,520
I'm also a rookie in this field.

65
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:38,110
It was Mr. Shao

66
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:40,080
who helped me immensely.

67
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,270
Both of us believe

68
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:45,270
hard work will lead to fruition.

69
00:03:47,390 --> 00:03:48,720
We all know

70
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:49,800
that Wei'er Hotel

71
00:03:49,910 --> 00:03:52,720
is a historic hotel.

72
00:03:57,750 --> 00:03:58,550
You're back.

73
00:03:58,550 --> 00:03:59,190
I'm back, An'an.

74
00:03:59,190 --> 00:04:00,240
You're here!

75
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:04,160
You bought so many things.

76
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:04,750
Yes.

77
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:06,270
I went on a shopping spree.

78
00:04:06,910 --> 00:04:08,190
Bring Mr. Wolf here too.

79
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:08,960
I have a present for him.

80
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:09,880
Okay.

81
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:13,670
What do you think?

82
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:17,070
I like the color.

83
00:04:17,670 --> 00:04:19,720
I heard there's a present for me?

84
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:20,830
Yes.

85
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,160
It got my attention right away.

86
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,720
I think it goes very well with your skin tone

87
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,550
and you can pair it with anything.

88
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:25,950
What do you think? I bought this for An'an.

89
00:04:27,070 --> 00:04:28,510
It's so...

90
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:29,200
Yes.

91
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:30,480
So practical.

92
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,830
I can put many things in it.

93
00:04:31,950 --> 00:04:33,200
I love it.

94
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,480
Mr. Wolf, this is for you.

95
00:04:36,670 --> 00:04:38,200
I think it suits you very well.

96
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:40,760
I know you usually wear luxury brands,

97
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:42,920
so you might not like it.

98
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:43,920
But it's okay

99
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,440
if you don't wear it.

100
00:04:45,550 --> 00:04:46,320
Don't feel obliged.

101
00:04:46,950 --> 00:04:47,790
Why are you laughing?

102
00:04:48,230 --> 00:04:49,270
I love it.

103
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,200
-Thanks, Lailai.
-Thank you.

104
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,270
Thank you.

105
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:53,390
You're welcome.

106
00:05:04,350 --> 00:05:06,880
An'an, you're on TV!

107
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:08,230
You look amazing.

108
00:05:09,790 --> 00:05:11,110
[Behind Wei'er Hotel's Acquisition]
Look at your eyes.

109
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,320
Commanding.

110
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:14,390
You shine like a star.

111
00:05:14,510 --> 00:05:15,510
Everyone kneels before you.

112
00:05:15,670 --> 00:05:17,200
You're exaggerating.

113
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,070
An'an.

114
00:05:18,070 --> 00:05:19,110
Did you have a script?

115
00:05:19,390 --> 00:05:20,320
No.

116
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,040
But when I was younger,

117
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,720
I always watched my father's interviews.

118
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,480
I picked up the skills like that.

119
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:28,000
Maybe it's a blessing.

120
00:05:28,230 --> 00:05:29,160
Let's head up.

121
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:34,830
Morning.

122
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:35,830
Morning, everyone.

123
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:36,950
Morning.

124
00:05:37,350 --> 00:05:38,110
An Yu.

125
00:05:38,550 --> 00:05:39,070
Well done!

126
00:05:41,110 --> 00:05:42,070
Jin Lailai.

127
00:05:42,670 --> 00:05:44,000
My coffee is here.

128
00:05:44,110 --> 00:05:45,200
It's downstairs.

129
00:05:45,270 --> 00:05:46,320
Fetch it for me, will you?

130
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:51,390
Can't you do it yourself?

131
00:05:52,110 --> 00:05:52,920
An Yu.

132
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:55,270
Just because you were offered a position
doesn't mean you can talk back.

133
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,160
Today is a good day.

134
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,390
Don't ruin it.

135
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:00,000
We're colleagues here.

136
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,390
No need to fuss over a petty matter.

137
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,390
Well...

138
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,230
It's okay.

139
00:06:03,230 --> 00:06:04,110
I'll fetch it for you.

140
00:06:04,110 --> 00:06:04,390
Just wait.

141
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:05,070
Su.

142
00:06:05,070 --> 00:06:05,880
It's okay.

143
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:09,950
Some people

144
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,950
just think too highly of themselves.

145
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:13,950
Without Shao Moli,

146
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,670
would you be interviewed?

147
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,950
You still need a man to be successful, after all.

148
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,760
Xu Jingya, what are you implying?

149
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,830
Stop being passive-aggressive.

150
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,200
I'm talking about you, An Yu.

151
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:28,440
I've been learning Muay Thai lately.

152
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,040
My coach said

153
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,950
my advantage

154
00:06:31,070 --> 00:06:32,720
was that I packed a strong punch.

155
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:34,270
But that

156
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:35,720
is also my drawback.

157
00:06:35,790 --> 00:06:37,200
I do not know how to control my strength.

158
00:06:45,070 --> 00:06:45,950
Lailai, An Yu.

159
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:53,070
I'm dropping by here

160
00:06:53,550 --> 00:06:54,790
to give you two gifts.

161
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,670
Thank you.

162
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:58,600
This is yours.

163
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:00,390
Thanks, Mr. Jiang.

164
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,830
Congratulations

165
00:07:03,550 --> 00:07:04,600
on getting a full-time position.

166
00:07:04,670 --> 00:07:05,640
Mr. Jiang.

167
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:06,880
Can I speak to you?

168
00:07:07,230 --> 00:07:08,000
What is it?

169
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:11,000
Let's talk over there.

170
00:07:18,510 --> 00:07:19,390
Your badge is inside.

171
00:07:19,390 --> 00:07:19,830
It's new.

172
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:20,720
Put it on.

173
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:29,040
An'an,

174
00:07:30,070 --> 00:07:31,200
I'll let you in on a secret.

175
00:07:31,670 --> 00:07:33,390
Su just told me

176
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:34,880
that we would still work together

177
00:07:34,950 --> 00:07:37,040
but in a different department.

178
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:39,320
I wonder if it's good or bad.

179
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:41,070
It's good, of course.

180
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:42,440
If I'm with you,

181
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:44,950
I can fight 100 Xu Jingyas.

182
00:07:45,350 --> 00:07:46,760
But I'm so nervous.

183
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:49,070
I wonder which department we will get.

184
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,480
An'an, which department do you want?

185
00:07:52,230 --> 00:07:54,320
If it's up to me,

186
00:07:54,550 --> 00:07:56,160
of course, I'll choose

187
00:07:56,790 --> 00:07:58,040
the Investment Department.

188
00:07:58,760 --> 00:08:00,070
So will I.

189
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:03,830
Unfortunately, Mr. Wolf
and Zhuoyue's partnership has ended.

190
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:06,200
If he could be the managing director of Zhuoyue,

191
00:08:06,390 --> 00:08:07,950
I would feel more reassured.

192
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:11,480
We have to rely on ourselves now.

193
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,480
No.

194
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:13,550
You're famous now.

195
00:08:13,550 --> 00:08:14,600
I'll rely on you.

196
00:08:17,110 --> 00:08:18,320
Keep a low profile.

197
00:08:18,550 --> 00:08:19,440
Okay.

198
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:21,950
Are you watching TV, my love?

199
00:08:27,460 --> 00:08:30,220
[Behind Wei'er Hotel's Acquisition]
(An Yu was the team leader.)

200
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:33,150
He's just a kid who returned from overseas.

201
00:08:33,880 --> 00:08:34,960
What's there to interview?

202
00:08:35,670 --> 00:08:37,320
He is quite humble

203
00:08:37,670 --> 00:08:39,550
and gives credit to An Yu.

204
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:42,790
[Behind Wei'er Hotel's Acquisition]
Everything is going well for An Yu now.

205
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,670
She has a stable job,

206
00:08:45,230 --> 00:08:46,520
a sizable income,

207
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:49,150
and the familial bond.

208
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:53,150
I'm sure she came back to fight
for Yiyi's custody.

209
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:56,790
Don't worry, Lulu.

210
00:08:58,350 --> 00:08:59,880
I plan to get in touch with Shao Moli

211
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,880
and bring him to our side.

212
00:09:02,150 --> 00:09:02,670
That way,

213
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:04,640
he can't help An Yu

214
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:07,520
and we will have one less competitor.

215
00:09:13,790 --> 00:09:14,470
Hello.

216
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,350
Mr. Fu.

217
00:09:17,550 --> 00:09:18,400
Of course.

218
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,230
I'm at home.

219
00:09:21,670 --> 00:09:22,470
Sure.

220
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,590
I'll introduce you to Mr. Chen

221
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:25,640
in two days.

222
00:09:25,670 --> 00:09:26,230
Is that all right?

223
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,790
An Yu?

224
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:44,150
An'an!

225
00:09:45,670 --> 00:09:47,400
Let's wait for the great news.

226
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:50,320
Mr. Fu is having this meeting with us.

227
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:52,880
Is he going to assign us to another department?

228
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,000
Should be.

229
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:55,520
Wei'er Hotel's project

230
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:56,840
was a huge success.

231
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,440
Based on my experience,

232
00:09:58,640 --> 00:09:59,230
we

233
00:09:59,230 --> 00:10:01,030
would be handsomely rewarded.

234
00:10:01,470 --> 00:10:02,030
A better project

235
00:10:02,030 --> 00:10:03,840
must be awaiting us.

236
00:10:05,710 --> 00:10:06,440
I see everyone's here.

237
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,230
Mr. Fu.

238
00:10:10,880 --> 00:10:11,790
We're having

239
00:10:11,790 --> 00:10:12,790
this meeting today

240
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:15,030
for a few announcements.

241
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:16,640
First,

242
00:10:16,760 --> 00:10:19,350
all of you performed exceptionally

243
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:21,030
on Wei'er Hotel's project.

244
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,320
Thanks to it,

245
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,320
An Yu and Jin Lailai

246
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,320
were offered full-time positions.

247
00:10:26,710 --> 00:10:27,760
On behalf of the company,

248
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,520
I would like to offer
my sincerest congratulations.

249
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:36,080
Since all of you have the potential
and the spirit now,

250
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,440
we have decided

251
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:38,440
to hand you

252
00:10:38,710 --> 00:10:40,350
the most challenging project

253
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:41,670
at the moment.

254
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,150
Mister,

255
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:52,840
is it very far away?

256
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:54,030
We're almost there.

257
00:10:58,090 --> 00:11:00,080
[Zhuoyue Finance, Chuanhe Branch]

258
00:11:11,030 --> 00:11:12,350
We have arrived.

259
00:11:15,230 --> 00:11:15,910
Let's go.

260
00:11:29,110 --> 00:11:30,790
Why did the driver leave?

261
00:11:31,150 --> 00:11:33,110
How are we supposed to go back later?

262
00:11:48,910 --> 00:11:49,880
Is there anyone here?

263
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:52,880
Is there anyone here?

264
00:12:17,670 --> 00:12:19,150
You must be the ones

265
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:20,550
exiled to this branch.

266
00:12:21,880 --> 00:12:22,960
I'm Li Zhou.

267
00:12:23,230 --> 00:12:23,960
L, I. Li.

268
00:12:24,230 --> 00:12:25,320
Z. H. O. U. Zhou.

269
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:28,230
You're the only staff member?

270
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:29,840
Did he just say exiled?

271
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:32,000
Zhuoyue has 37 branches

272
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,590
in Yuqing.

273
00:12:33,760 --> 00:12:36,000
Every month, the worst performing branch
will be eliminated.

274
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,470
And this branch

275
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:38,840
has always come last place.

276
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:40,790
All my colleagues left.

277
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:42,670
I'm the only one here.

278
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:44,910
The headquarter did not
send more people here either.

279
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:49,880
I feel bad for you.

280
00:12:50,030 --> 00:12:51,150
There, there.

281
00:12:51,520 --> 00:12:53,640
I like your bunny.

282
00:12:54,030 --> 00:12:55,280
Where did you get it?

283
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:56,550
Toss me the link.

284
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,080
You like it?

285
00:12:59,230 --> 00:13:00,030
It's yours then.

286
00:13:00,640 --> 00:13:01,200
For real?

287
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:02,520
Thank you.

288
00:13:02,520 --> 00:13:03,320
