In that case,

501
00:23:18,950 --> 00:23:21,100
raising a child sure costs a lot of money.

502
00:23:21,430 --> 00:23:23,740
A child can spend much more money than an adult.

503
00:23:25,140 --> 00:23:27,100
Have you looked into

504
00:23:27,430 --> 00:23:28,860
education funds?

505
